idea-plugin.description:
      Auto-Align allows you to align your code with a pretty print alignment
      <br>
      <br>
      SHORTCUT : (windows/linux) CONTROL+OPTION+I (mac) CMD+OPTION+I
      <br>
      <br>
      EXAMPLE :
      <br>
      <pre>
var hi={
  field : 'val',
  heel: 'red'
};
var hi    = {
  field    : 'val',
  heel     : 'red'
};
      <pre>
